About Us
Founded in 2002, Broadcast Pix is a Boston-based company that creates integrated production switchers, as well as cloud-based solutions for media management, collaboration, and distribution.

Our tailored solutions provide the best tools for any production environment, from compact mobile units to large-scale control rooms, and our BPswitch product line utilizes the power of our BPnet IP ecosystem to allow users to Take Control of live productions from across town or across the world. With our user-friendly, customizable control systems, it’s easy for anyone to produce great live video, even with minimal training. 

Every Broadcast Pix system features patented automation and innovative tools to deliver a complete user experience. We optimize the production process through data, AI, cloud-based technologies, and image analysis, and our quality workmanship ensures robust and reliable systems for studio and mobile applications. 

With more than 4,500 installations across more than 100 countries, our approach remains focused on our clients – identify their needs, improve their workflows, and reduce their capital and operating costs. 




For more information on Broadcast Pix, check out the product and solution pages of this website, or contact us below.



Broadcast Pix, Inc. 

