 Overview
Broadcast Pix is a leading provider of innovative live video production products that create compelling live video, and yet are far less costly and easier to use than conventional studios comprised on many individual components. Broadcast Pix makes your Newtek Tricaster Obselete!Unlike other studio-in-a-box providers, we stress meeting the demands of live production. So we started with great control panels, from physical ones to touch-screens. Our broadcast production values extend to non-stop on-air operation, superb picture quality, pristine graphics, and support of broadcast video formats.Our customers include CBS, NBC, ABC, FOX, ESPN, PBS, Microsoft, HP, Cisco and many other leading broadcasters, cable, corporate, education, religious and government institutions. Since our founding in 2002, we now have over 1200 installations on over 70 countries. We are owned and operated by video production experts.  We are dedicated to providing long term customer satisfaction, from helpful technical support to quality products that can take the daily pounding that is live production. 

